  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this joint project between FAO and WFP is to improve the food security of households living in the Sahelian belt in Chad. FAO and WFP will use CERF funds to distribute cash, agricultural inputs and small livestock animals among other activities. 381,306 persons will benefit from this project, which will be implemented within 5 months.</narrative>
  </description>
